videos.description: Tra Holder brings the ball up the court and splashes home a 3-pointer for the Sun Devils in the first half.
videos.headline: Arizona State's Holder on target from deep

videos.description: Justin Bibbins hits his defender with a fake pass and drills the shot from beyond the arc for the Utes.
videos.headline: Utah's Bibbins drains 3-pointer

videos.description: Shannon Evans II puts the moves on his defender and knocks down a 3-pointer for the Sun Devils in the second half.
videos.headline: Arizona State's Evans hits sick crossover, drills 3-pointer

videos.description: Remmy Martin gets the ASU faithful on their feet with a deep 3-pointer in the second half.
videos.headline: Arizona State's Martin sinks big 3-pointer

videos.description: Remmy Martin capitalizes on a Utah turnover and takes it all the way to the rack for the lead in the second half.
videos.headline: Arizona State's Martin gives Sun Devils the lead

videos.description: ASU's Curtain of Distraction opens to reveal a large man with an even larger wrecking ball.
videos.headline: Arizona State's Curtain of Distraction is hilarious

videos.description: Tra Holder ends an exciting sequence of shot attempts, blocks, and loose balls with a mid-range jumper for the Sun Devils.
videos.headline: Arizona State's Holder sinks jumper on wild play
